  "text": "haloplanktis and V. fischeri for Na+ for the transport of a number of metabolizable compounds. Careful [CITATION_1] ,000 x g (4\u00b0C) for 10 min and washed 3 times with volumes of complete salts-Tris (CST) buffers equal to the volume of the original medium. These buffers contained 50 mM Tris; 50 mM MgSO4; 9 mM KCl; 1 mM KH2PO4 (omitted from 32Pi experiments); and combinations of choline chloride (ChCl), NaCl, KCl, or LiCl totaling 300 mM, as required for the different experimental conditions. The pH was adjusted to 7.2 with HCl. Concentrated stock cell suspensions were prepared from the washed cells and maintained on ice during the course of an experiment.",
